parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning Auto Stop/Start feature can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off unexpectedly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off at red lights or stop signs
fails to restart
requires multiple attempts to restart
and may cause the driver to be rear-ended or stuck in traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system malfunctions can cause various safety issues, such as airbag malfunctions, loss of heating and air conditioning, and failure of critical systems like the brakes and steering.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on and off
the passenger seat airbag is activated when no one is sitting
the seatbelt alert goes off when no one is in the seat
the automatic lights don't turn on
and the radio won't turn off when the engine is turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Reduced Engine Power and Engine Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The reduced engine power and engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences reduced engine power
stalls
or fails to start
and may display warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The HVAC system failure can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, and may lead to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioner or heater fails to work
and the blower motor stops functioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The key stuck in the ignition can prevent the vehicle from being turned off, increasing the risk of theft and leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition cylinder
preventing the vehicle from being turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine and reduced power can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power while driving
the check engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle jerks or surges while driving
the engine makes a loud noise
and the vehicle is unable to maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto start/stop feature can cause accidents, especially when driving in heavy traffic, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off and does not restart
the vehicle stalls while driving
the auto start/stop feature does not engage properly
and the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the variable valve timing system can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine warning light is illuminated
the engine makes a loud noise
the vehicle surges or jerks while driving
and the vehicle is unable to maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rocker Arm Oil Control Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rocker arm oil control valve can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine warning light is illuminated
the engine makes a loud noise
the vehicle surges or jerks while driving
and the vehicle is unable to maintain speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto stop/start feature can cause the vehicle to stall or not restart, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to restart after auto stop
the engine turns over endlessly without success
and the vehicle may shut off without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to hesitate, stall, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates or slips
the vehicle loses power
the transmission module fails
and the vehicle may stall or hesitate to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rocker Arm Oil Control Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rocker arm oil control valve can cause the engine to stall or not restart, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to restart
the check engine light illuminates
and the vehicle may experience power loss or hesitation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift to park system can cause the vehicle to drain the battery, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a "shift to park" message
the battery drains
and the vehicle may not shut off completely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle position sensor can cause the vehicle to lose power or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates
the vehicle loses power or hesitates
and the throttle position sensor code is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the high pressure fuel pump can cause the engine to stall or not restart, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails to restart
the check engine light illuminates
and the vehicle may experience power loss or hesitation.
